channel.title: Can someone explain why my server isn't working properly?
channel.description:
hello,
i've recently been trying to get on my server and i can get on fine, but i keep thinking huh? how come no-ones on... then my friend told me he couldn't get on/trying for like 10 minutes. These are the programmes i've run... no-ip-----himachi-----source----compiler------runserver-----mopar.... and i logged on.. but none of my friends could. can someone please help me?
If i have done something wrong someone tell me please ( i dont think i have ) i do this process all the time. my server was on yesterday.
my internet is connected properly... so someone tell me plz.
i know u might be thinking " omg wot a noob " but... if someone fixes my problem then there is a 500k reward.
